<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id747fda88-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s50305"><num value="50305">§ 50305.</num><heading> Exclusive right to name</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The corporation and its State and local subdivisions have the exclusive right to use the name “Disabled American Veterans”.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id747fda89-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7">(<ref href="/us/pl/105/225">Pub. L. 105–225</ref>, <date date="1998-08-12">Aug. 12, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/1344">112 Stat. 1344</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
